text: Alikovskoye Rural Settlement (; , Elĕk jal tărăkhĕ) is an administrativeIn accordance with Law #28, the municipal divisions in the Chuvash Republic are considered to be its administrative-territorial divisions and municipal division (a rural settlement) of Alikovsky District of the Chuvash Republic, Russia.Law #37 It is in the central part of the district. Its administrative center is the locality (a selo) of Alikovo. Rural settlement's population: 4,291 (2006 est.). Alikovskoye Rural Settlement comprises ten rural localities. The Cheboksary–Yadrin and the Cheboksary–Krasnye Chetai highways cross the territory of the rural settlement. ==References== ===Notes=== ===Sources=== * * ==Further reading== *L. A.
